    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Roman calendars, including works on parchment and also works inscribed in stone and displayed for the public; fasti indicated dates of festivals, games, days allowed for legal business, anniversaries of historical events, and other notable dates.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
